sg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ccb32f25841b4170dd818811286165554b20e191","tid":110794,"uid":76681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁又未必，有啲人可能需要逗留係台灣超過30日，所以要親自去金鐘整，同網上申請即時批唔同既。<br />\n我估張圖既意思係咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我講<span style=\"color: red;\">真香港人</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請定義"},{"pid":"2cb4f3cfcce159c48f18df44301866ec42de5a17","tid":110794,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:16:33.000Z","msg":"樓上一班支那種<br />\n利申咩香港出世<br />\n睇死又咪老母老豆係支那種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:元朗居民"},{"pid":"4bd59fcf4cf7efb998c7dd8e30e938a84f093511","tid":110794,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:19:39.000Z","msg":"如果係英治時期，由港英正常批准入香港而又認同香港文化嘅人，我諗連登仔都接受係香港人。<br />\n<br />\n係宜家連蝗都叫做香港人，走來屌香港人嘅，先仆街冚家剷。<br />\n<br />\n不過，睇個新政策，台灣政府應該幾歡迎佢地去消費。$$$"},{"pid":"65acb3f6db472cc2f14192a3cfbd9f57f6e5ccf9","tid":110794,"uid":54878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:23:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>新界嘅鄉紳全部香港出世，全部奶共<br />\n我老豆大陸出世，極度反共<br />\n利申：以前係地主家族<br />\n<br />\n明白未呀，攞香港出世打飛機嘅連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係你覺得你哋啲大陸仔反共就唔係大陸仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜撚野logic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你敢話你祖宗18代都香港出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁雙非落來生嘅仔就係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人真心冇資格講血統論囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3867026975480531587873b20684568be4cc1b","tid":110794,"uid":13678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:23:33.000Z","msg":"當呢到係 uwants MK壇 mw 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334de13383e8cec0c1943a2ee27dffdfcb5c0d3b","tid":110794,"uid":77199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:23:40.000Z","msg":"上年去台灣 我大陸出世(3歲落黎香港) <br />\n永久居民身份證拎左十幾年<br />\n香港出世既不嬲都上網做就得<br />\n但我地呢d大陸落黎但純正廣東話口音既 就要特登朝早去金鐘交表做證 <br />\n雖然去左一次之後唔駛再去金鐘交表 上網搞就得 <br />\n轉左上網搞係方便左"},{"pid":"68fac0a82c97c695632ec23a7ec081266f730a22","tid":110794,"uid":42434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:32:16.000Z","msg":"支那蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601f475178138abc864ab03e546b7279ebf94cad","tid":110794,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:34:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/m0yvk9cl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fm0yvk9cl&h=34ccbd34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知點解唔覺有人講/新聞有提過<br />\n只要有香港身份證又無BNO/其他外國護照<br />\n無論係咪香港出世<br />\n都可以網上搞入台證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講返單野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仆街啦真係！屌！"},{"pid":"9cbe869fb413de8934d852033046a720a368e25b","tid":110794,"uid":5480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:37:10.000Z","msg":"原來大陸出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4bb225f87074707150d48598d2a8a28ba386e6a","tid":110794,"uid":72733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:38:54.000Z","msg":"雖然我都唔鍾意大陸人某啲令人厭惡嘅事<br />\n例如啲細路隨街大小便 走水貨<br />\n但唔係所有大陸人都係衰嘅<br />\n係未了解樓主呢個人之前<br />\n就咁話人哋蝗種似乎有啲以偏概全<br />\n加上呢個詞語本身帶有歧視或攻擊嘅意思<br />\n咁樣話人係咪盲目咁為反而反呢"},{"pid":"62fae5fb4143d8dae53869de15b2f8107c4af859","tid":110794,"uid":72733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:39:38.000Z","msg":"利申：土生土長香港人"}]}